:css
  ul li{
    list-style-position: outside;
    }
  p.q, p.a{
    width: 50%;
    float: left;
  }
  h1.about{
    background-color: transparent;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-top: 120px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    width: 38%;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 100px;
    margin-left: 0;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .about_us{
    background-image: image-url("105H.jpg");
    background-size: cover;
    width: 100%;
    height: 200%;
  }
  .faqs{
    padding-bottom: 40px
  }
  strong{
    display: inline;
  }
  .row{
    padding-bottom: 20px;
  }

.about_us
  .row
    .medium-12.columns
      %h1.about 
        %strong
          We've been in your shoes. 

.row 
  .medium-12.columns
    %br
    %h2 About Us
    %p{:style => "display: inline"} We are building a trusted community for students to find and learn more about internships. We've experienced the recruiting process and truly hope we help make the process more transparent and less stressful for 
    %strong
      you. 

.row 
  .medium-12.columns
    %h2 How it Works
    %p You're looking for an internship at a competitive firm. To learn more about what's out there, you can look through reviews of companies your friends have worked at and  connect with past interns to ask more in-depth questions. If you write a review of a company you've worked at, we will share your resume with top startup CEOs and recruiters. Explore the world beyond what you know. 

.row
  .medium-12.columns.faqs
    %h3 FAQs
    .question
      %p.q Q: Why submit a review? 
      %p.a A: If you submit a review, you will then be able to submit a resume to our partnering companies for another internship.
    .question
      %p.q Q: Will companies see my review?
      %p.a A: No, they will not see your review. Only students with @college.harvard.edu email accounts will be able to see your review.
    .question
      %p.q Q: Are my reviews anonymous?
      %p.a A: No, reviews are not anonymous. We want to create a transparent, trusting community, and believe that students should be able to connect with past interns. 
    .question
      %p.q Q: Will others be able to see my resume? 
      %p.a A: No, only employers will be able to see your resume. For other questions about privacy, please check out our Privacy Policy.
    .question
      %p.q Q: More questions? 
      %p.a A: Contact us and we'll help you out. 


     

     